Taken from the old final,

I have made some changes around the map,

There is now 2 more end game at the end of the map these are: BHOP and AWP.

Most of the trap have had tweaks to make this a little harder but not to hard that it can't be finished.

Give credit to MrLate for creating a great map that people enjoy,

This is a fix with some nice changes.

Hope you guys and girls enjoy the map.

Any problem please comment below and i be sure to help or fix what is wrong.
